main event: A small light was sighted hovering or moving slowly overhead in Keystone Heights, Florida.
interesting points: The object was visible for about 30 seconds and did not resemble any known aircraft or object., The object accelerated out of sight in a southeastern direction., No sound was heard during the observation., The visibility of the object led to several witnesses, including a naval officer., Initial investigation suggested it might have been a satellite, although no definitive conclusion was reached.
sighted object: a small light in the sky
